metadata.name: Myth⛩️ #1
metadata.description: Re:Myth is a brand that reinterprets the myths into the Web 3.0 culture. Our brand originated from the idea that reinterpretation is the key to seeing and reading stories from a different point of view. The Re:Myth collection is composed of several Japanese myths such as Amaterasu and Tsukuyomi. Different myths will be released along the way till our mint.
